		             [6,	23,	1,	'English/Literature',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped, and the campus buildings are built with a variety of materials and architectural styles. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The interior classrooms are filled with cheap chair-desks made of wood and plastic. One wing of the building is dedicated to faculty offices, but most of them appear to have been vacated recently.'],
