		             [7,	22,	1,	'E. Tobias Hawking Library',	'Library',	'This is an imposing building built of red brick. The middle section of the building is a ten-storey tower. Sheets of paper swirl down the street in the wind.',	'Books are stacked haphazardly everywhere. Several archive shelves have been knocked over.'],
		             [7,	23,	1,	'E. Tobias Hawking Library',	'Library',	'This is an imposing building built of red brick. This wing of the library is the oldest part of the structure, and was due for renovation. Sheets of paper swirl down the street in the wind.',	'Books are stacked haphazardly everywhere. Several archive shelves have been knocked over.'],
		             [7,	24,	1,	'Business Administration',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped, and the campus buildings are built with a variety of materials and architectural styles. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The interior classrooms are newly furnished and lit with tactfully placed uplights. A large student commons room contains a long screen that was clearly once a stock ticker, but has since gone dark.'],
