		             [7,	35,	1,	'Traveller\'s Inn',	'Hotel',	'This is a largish building featuring a faux rustic facade, built directly into the airport terminal. The stark contrast makes the inn look rather gaudy and cheap.',	'A humble lobby at the entrance gives way to stairwells and elevators here, both leading to rooms which are simple, spartan and for the most part, identical. You find yourself easily lost in the winding, identical corridors.'],
