		             [7,	37,	1,	'Sidney Int\'l Medical Clinic',	'Hospital',	'This is a small medical clinic built into the airport building, constructed fairly recently. It seems it served as a staging area for travellers who became ill but couldn\'t be moved to the mainland right away.',	'The medical clinic is fairly small, but sleek and modern. A small pharmacy for airport travellers is located in the clinic\'s lobby.'],
