		             [8,	19,	0,	'Beach',	'Beach',	'This beach has fine brown sand. Waves lap gently on the shore. Some driftwood can occasionally be spotted. One patch of beach is littered with empty bottles, cigarettes and other signs of a recent party.',	''],
		             [8,	20,	1,	'Northern Dorms',	'Apartment Building',	'This building is five stories tall and made of aged brick. It has several wings that are asymmetrical to one another and appear to have been constructed at different times. A large concrete staircase ascends to a grand, stone-arched entrance set into what appears to be the oldest part of the building.',	'Despite the building\'s aged exterior, the interior has clearly been recently renovated, and the lights, paint and fixtures are all very new. The dorm rooms themselves are very small and cluttered, but are nevertheless comfortable and surprisingly well-lit.'],
		             [8,	21,	1,	'Art & Music',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped, and the campus buildings are built with a variety of materials and architectural styles. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The interior art studios are filled with easels, still-life props and half-finished student artwork. The studios on the top floor are cluttered with architectural drawings and building models that appear to have been printed out of a clear plastic resin.'],
		             [8,	22,	1,	'E. Tobias Hawking Library',	'Library',	'This is an imposing building built of red brick. This wing of the library contains most of the university archives, and the facade has been renovated recently. Sheets of paper swirl down the street in the wind.',	'Books are stacked haphazardly everywhere. Several archive shelves have been knocked over.'],
		             [8,	23,	1,	'MegaBites',	'Restaurant',	'The building appears to be a restaurant, constructed fairly recently. Despite appearing to be closed, the aroma of freshly-cooked food wafts from the entrance of the building.',	'Several tables and chairs are placed about the place and there is a large kitchen in the back. Several large televisions hang from the walls, which are decorated with jerseys and photographs of various sporting feats accomplished by Cimmerian University student athletes.'],
