		             [8,	27,	0,	'Cimmerian Forest',	'Forest',	'This area is dominated by the trunks of tall evergreen trees. The undergrowth is damp and thick with moss and ferns. A small, solitary grave marker juts out of the ground on the edge of the forest, near the pond. The words on its surface have been eroded away over time.',	'You walk through tunnels left over from the demon incursion of Elysium, here they appear to have built themselves a supply area, much of which they left behind when they were driven out.'],
		             [8,	28,	0,	'Cimmerian Field',	'Grassland',	'This area is filled with tall grass that flows and whispers in the breeze. It is crisscrossed with recreation trails for walking and bicycling, as well as the occasional bench or picnic table. A building once stood here, but all that is left is its stone foundation, now covered in moss.',	''],
