		             [9,	19,	1,	'Northern Dorms',	'Apartment Building',	'This building is five stories tall and made of aged brick. It has two wings that wrap around each other to shelter a tree-lined courtyard containing a series of concrete sculptures of students at study and at play.',	'The lobby and stairs show signs of having been recently painted and renovated, but the hallways and dorms themselves, while homey, are showing signs of their age. Each door bears the handwritten names of students who lived there, indicating that the dorm was divided into separate wings for men and women.'],
		             [9,	20,	1,	'Northern Dorms',	'Apartment Building',	'This building is five stories tall and made of aged brick that is almost entirely overrun with vines and ivy. Colorful athletic pennants hang in many of the cast iron windows.',	'The hallways and stairwells of this building are narrow and the carpets and paint are fading, but the doors and security systems appear to be state-of-the-art. The ceilings in the dorm rooms themselves are very high, and some contain impromptu lofts that the residents had built for themselves.'],
		             [9,	21,	1,	'Belmont Power',	'Power Plant',	'Power lines radiate from a large, imposing brick building. Many different colors and patterns of brick indicate that it has been renovated many times, and part of the facade is clearly very new.',	'Several large generators sit inside the building.'],
