		             [10,	18,	1,	'Education',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped, and the campus buildings are built with a variety of materials and architectural styles. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The hallways are decorated with the covers of well-known children\'s books and colorful, splashy posters promoting the role of teachers to emerging minds. Most of the classrooms are teaching laboratories furnished and decorated in a facsimile of a typical elementary school classroom.'],
		             [10,	19,	1,	'Administration of Justice',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped, and the campus buildings are built with a variety of materials and architectural styles. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The interior classrooms are filled with cheap chair-desks made of wood and plastic. A small but apparently well-frequented law library can be found on the first floor.'],
		             [10,	20,	1,	'Northern Dorms',	'Apartment Building',	'This building is ten stories tall and made of grey concrete panels with small, square windows. A series of colorful hand-painted murals bearing the nicknames of each dorm floor stretches up one side of the building.',	'The lobby area has high concrete ceilings and is strewn with aged tables and chairs for studying. The dorms are cramped and cluttered, but surprisingly comfortable.'],
		             [10,	21,	1,	'Administration Building',	'University',	'The grounds surrounding this imposing, classically-inspired building are immaculately manicured and landscaped. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The hallways of this building have high ceilings and marble finishes, and every footstep has a resounding echo. Most of the offices within are more cheaply furnished and dedicated to handling bureaucratic paperwork related to academic life.'],
		             [10,	22,	1,	'Student Activity Center',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped, and the campus buildings are built with a variety of materials and architectural styles. Several park benches dot the area. This building has a large bell tower, stopped at noon or midnight.',	'This building appears to have been renovated and expanded many times, and is mostly dedicated to office space for student clubs and meeting rooms of various sizes for hosting events. A bowling alley and a small movie theater can be found in the basement.'],
		             [10,	23,	1,	'Charlotte\'s Bakery - University',	'Bakery',	'This is a small, simple building which once sold baked goods. A plaque on the outside reveals this bakery is named for one of the daughters of a famous early settler of this land.',	'There is a hand-painted menu and a glass display of various baked goods for sale. The furnishings are eclectic, and the walls are lined with the work of local artists and signed photographs of visiting celebrities.'],
