		             [11,	19,	1,	'Political Science',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped. Many of the buildings facing the park have a monolithic concrete style and appear to have been built at the same time. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The interior classrooms are full of cheap chair-desks made of wood and plastic. Many of the rooms on the first floor appear to have been cleaned recently and poorly, and the remains of Halloween decorations are strewn about the area.'],
		             [11,	20,	1,	'Science & Engineering',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped. Many of the buildings facing the park have a monolithic concrete style and appear to have been built at the same time. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The hallways of this building are decorated with large, colorful displays of various graduate research projects. Most of the building is dedicated to laboratories, though there are many small, eclectically furnished classrooms and a large central auditorium.'],
		             [11,	21,	1,	'Cimmerian University Police Department',	'Police Station',	'This is a tree-lined concrete building about four stores tall, ringed by the same walking paths and park benches as the surrounding university. Several squad cars are parked behind the station, and a large City Police Department logo is stamped on the facade.',	'There are several service counters dedicated to student services such as parking tickets and lost bicycles. Nevertheless, most of the interior appears to have been used by officers deployed for serious investigation and surveillance, and the armory is well-stocked.'],
		             [11,	22,	1,	'University Medical Clinic',	'Hospital',	'This medical center consists of several interconnected buildings that appear to have been built of different materials and at different times. The signage and landscaping is consistent with the rest of the university.',	'This appears to have been a teaching hospital for training medical students. Nevertheless, much of the first two floors of the building is taken up by a sports-medicine facility that smells of sweat and is filled with exotic exercise equipment.'],
