		             [12,	4,	1,	'Ministry of Energy',	'Office Building',	'This is a sequence of interconnected square buildings of stark grey concrete, all but one of which appear to have been built at the same time. They wrap around three sides of a large planted courtyard which contains displays of several emerging alternative energy systems.',	'The interior shows some signs of age but is spacious and surprisingly comfortable. Much more of the interior is devoted to meeting rooms, conference rooms and auditoriums than actual offices.'],
		             [12,	5,	1,	'Ministry of Social Development',	'Office Building',	'The facade of this four-story building is made of crisscrossed white metal slats that have mostly been arranged to block sun but form the shape of several human figures on one side. The grounds are expansive, tree-lined and manicured.',	'The lobby contains a greeting sign that repeats itself in twenty different languages. The offices are spacious and well-organized, and pictures and presentations suggest that many of them were used for planning festivals and cultural events.'],
		             [12,	6,	1,	'Ministry of Health',	'Office Building',	'This is a curved glass building about twelve stories high, with a large parking lot and minimalist landscaping. A large auditorium can be found to one side.',	'The offices here are filled with papers and electronics, yet most have been neatly organized and some show signs of being newly occupied after being vacated for some time. The basement floors contain several state-of-the-art laboratories filled with complex testing equipment.'],
