		             [12,	22,	1,	'University Medical Clinic',	'Pharmacy',	'This medical center consists of several interconnected buildings that appear to have been built of different materials and at different times. The signage and landscaping is consistent with the rest of the university.',	'This is a pharmacy and urgent-care clinic that treated common student ailments. Much of the interior consists of exam rooms plastered in colorful informational posters that offer advice on healthy student living. '],
