		             [13,	5,	1,	'Ministry of Justice',	'Office Building',	'This granite-clad tower stands noticeably taller than any other building on the island. A large antenna is located on the roof, but none of the lights positioned atop it are functioning.',	'A skylit atrium containing a bank of glass elevators can be found at the center of this building. A statue of a woman holding a pair of scales stands at its center, though it appears to have been added fairly recently.'],
		             [13,	6,	1,	'Ministry of National Defense',	'Office Building',	'This building is six stories tall and finished in plain white stone. The main entrance is framed by columns but lacks any other ornamentation.',	'The interiors of this building are a dramatic contrast between large rooms crammed with cluttered workstations and several clean, stately private offices. The phones in several of the latter offices are blinking to indicate recent missed calls.'],
