		             [13,	9,	1,	'Library of Parliament',	'Library',	'This three-story granite building is built in imitation of the neo-Baroque style of Parliament, though it was clearly constructed much more recently. A few of the small windows that line the ground floor have been broken.',	'Most of the library is filled with densely packed archives that were once accessed via an automated system that no longer functions. The third floor contains a large, spacious reading room with excellent views of the Inner Harbor.'],
		             [13,	10,	1,	'Civil Guard Headquarters',	'Police Station',	'The flags of Laurentia and several branches of the Civil Guard gendarmerie fly in front of this four-story brick building. There is a large motor pool behind the station, but most squad cars and other vehicles appear to be elsewhere.',	'The station is clean and neat, and contains facilities for training and equipping a city-wide gendarmerie. The basement contains a situation room lined with flickering electronic maps of Laurentia and the surrounding seas. There are occasional loud sirens and flashes of emergency lights, but the facility\'s communication system offers no further clue as to their cause.'],
