		             [13,	17,	1,	'Industrial Technology',	'Factory',	'This is a long, three-sort building finished in curved glass on one face and grey concrete on the others. A large, square industrial laboratory frames one end of the building.',	'The interior consists of a sequence of concrete workspaces filled with heavy industrial equipment, and the hallways are filled with colorful posters describing graduate research projects in robotics and industrial engineering. A large industrial laboratory contains cranes and other equipment for heavy construction.'],
		             [13,	18,	1,	'Industrial Technology',	'University',	'This is a long, three-storybuilding finished in curved glass on one face and grey concrete on the others.',	'The interior consists of a sequence of concrete workspaces filled with heavy industrial equipment, and the hallways are filled with colorful posters describing graduate research projects in robotics and industrial engineering.'],
		             [13,	19,	1,	'Computer Science',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped, and the campus buildings are built with a variety of materials and architectural styles. Several park benches dot the area.',	'This building appears to have been renovated much more recently than most of the rest of the campus, with brand-new modular furniture and pristine, modern interiors. The classrooms have state-of-the-art electronics and have movable glass partitions to form larger or smaller spaces.'],
		             [13,	20,	1,	'Science & Engineering',	'University',	'The grounds are immaculately manicured and landscaped, and the campus buildings are built with a variety of materials and architectural styles. Several park benches dot the area.',	'The hallways of this building are decorated with large, colorful displays of various graduate research projects. Most of the building is dedicated to laboratories, though there are many small, eclectically furnished classrooms and a large central auditorium.'],
		             [13,	21,	1,	'Auxiliary Services',	'University',	'This sprawling concrete building has several entrances and loading docks and is surrounded by a large parking lot filled with vehicles bearing the Cimmerian University insignia. A small enclosed shelter for a bus stop can be found here.',	'The interior contains a variety of services in support of the functioning of the University, ranging from printing to catering to building maintenance. There are several maps posted of the interior, which appear to have been created at different times and often disagree with each other.'],
		             [13,	22,	1,	'Southern Dorms',	'Apartment Building',	'This building is seven stories tall and made of new brick, with a weatherized metal roof that reflects nearby light. The windows on the top two floors are tinted and lack the colorful decorations that can be found adorning windows throughout the rest of the building.',	'The hallways and dorm rooms are spacious and comfortable, with modern fixtures and new paint and carpets. The security system appears to be state-of-the-art, and the doors are surprisingly heavy and sturdy.'],
		             [13,	23,	1,	'Southern Dorms',	'Apartment Building',	'This building is about a dozen stories tall and made of brick and concrete, with large bay windows. A ribbon of glass curtain wall on one side of the building marks the location of the elevator lobby.',	'The lobby is spacious and appears to be newer than the rest of the building, with many large and small spaces for studying and events. The dorm rooms themselves are small and surprisingly neat, and appear to have housed only one student each.'],
		             [13,	24,	1,	'Southern Dorms',	'Apartment Building',	'This building is eight stories tall and made of glass and new brick in a variety of colors and patterns. The windows glisten in the sun and are filled with posters and colorful athletic pennants. The lobby of the dorm is a large, glassed-in atrium.',	'The lobby is surprisingly clean and furnished with new, brightly-colored chairs and sofas. There is a mezzanine with a state-of-the-art fitness center. The dorm rooms themselves are small but comfortable, and are cluttered with piles of clothing and eclectic personal decor.'],
