		             [14,	19,	1,	'Paragon',	'Office Building',	'This building is a cube roughly a dozen stories tall, clad in anodized aluminum panels with extensive use of tinted structural glass. A large, illuminated corporate logo is set into the side of the building in lieu of signage.',	'The finishes and furnishings are modular, modern and colored almost entirely in white, black and grey, though colorful product design proposals for bionic augmentations can be found displayed on the panelized walls of conference rooms. The building\'s signage appears to have its own unique family of fonts.'],
		             [14,	20,	1,	'Rho Rho Phi',	'Apartment Building',	'It is a four-story brick lodge with stone trim and faux-historical half timbering. One wing in the rear of the building appears to have been constructed much more recently than the rest.',	'The commons area and bedrooms are comfortable and rather expensively furnished, although bottles, party leftovers and other litter can be found cluttering many of the rooms. The halls are decorated with large, framed group photographs of young men and women that date back four decades.'],
		             [14,	21,	1,	'Delta Nu Delta',	'Apartment Building',	'This is a broad, three-story brick building with wrought-iron windows and a weathered slate roof. The name of the fraternity is etched into a large stone sign in front of a wide, tree-lined lawn.',	'The first floor is a commons room with a large fireplace, a pool table, and heavy wooden furniture. A curved staircase ascends to upper floors that are largely composed of small, cluttered bedrooms. The coat of arms of the fraternity features prominently in the decor throughout.'],
