		             [15,	5,	1,	'Ministry of Industry',	'Office Building',	'It is a square six-story building of plain white concrete. The grounds are extensively landscaped and contain several walking paths and picnic benches, while parking space can be found in a concrete ramp that is nearly as tall as the building itself.',	'The lobby is lined with an extensive historical display that highlights notable events in Laurentian business and industry through the years. The offices and meeting rooms are compact and appear to have gone at least forty years without significant renovations.'],
