		             [19,	19,	1,	'Resistor Systems',	'Office Building',	'The building is about two dozen stories tall and is made of glass and steel. Its facade shimmers in the light, though none of its offices show signs of occupation from the outside. A small enclosed shelter for a bus stop can be found here.',	'A clean, simple lobby area leads to higher floors, which are filled with empty, cobweb ridden cubicles. The elevators no longer work, and the stairwells are littered with papers.'],
