		             [20,	19,	1,	'Olympic Tower',	'Skyscraper',	'This enormous, imposing building, by far the tallest in the city, is over a hundred stories tall. The tower dwarfs everything nearby, and the top is dominated by a large glassed-in aperture that spans the width of the building. The tower reflects enough light that it appears to glow slightly at all hours of the day.',	'This is the tower\'s lobby. Numerous electronic security checkpoints, now deactivated and unmanned, sit idle. They serve as barriers between the main lobby area and the elevators, none of which function. No stairwells are visible. An ornate fresco, depicting a divine struggle between good and evil, decorates the walls and ceiling.'],
